schools.name: Galileo School Of Math And Science

data.description: Charming tri-level home in a well-established neighborhood offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. This 4-bed, 2-bath residence boasts a meticulously maintained interior with an updated kitchen featuring stainless appliances, tile floors, and modern cabinets. The updated bathrooms showcase contemporary tile, vanities, and brushed nickel hardware. Enjoy the spacious master bedroom with two closets, including a walk-in. The lower level features a generous family room, perfect for gatherings. Updated doors and trim throughout add a touch of elegance. With a one-car garage and a sizable backyard, this property is a delightful haven for those seeking a cozy and modern retreat.
